Clear day- algae blooms- weeds showing.
Ice off about 1 month- ducks and geese are on the lake.
Very warm- weeds are growing rapidly on the lake- boat traffic was heavy over the weekend.
Partly cloudy- windy and high weeds.
Partly cloudy- muskrats- trees are turning color- winds are calm.
Partly cloudy- 58 degrees- no plant growth- too early.
North bay secchi was 11 feet.  Partly cloudy- lots of floating weeds.
Full sunlight- weeds heavy- lake is calm.
Clear- cool- 48 degrees- weeds are down.
Clear- ice out three weeks- no weed growth yet.
Clear-sunny.  Few weeds. 2 3/4" rain since 6/17/96.  Water cold 66 degrees F 3' level.
Partly cloudy-moderate wind-high weeds-presently are harvesting weeds.
Partly cloudy- warm.  Weeds low.  Rain gauge reading from 6/2 to 6/25=2.75 inches.
Partly cloudy.  70 degrees.  Weeds remain low.
Algal- weeds high- muskrats active- 2 inch rain between 8/14/97-8/27/97
Clear and sunny.  Early weeds.  Saw muskrats.
Partly cloudy and windy.  Some high weeds.
Partly cloudy and windy.  Two inches of rain in the last two weeks.
Cloudy.  1 1/2 inches of rain in the last three days.
Clear blue sky- 60 F- light wind- no algae- low weeds
Clear blue sky- no wind- no algae- weeds are getting higher + being cut.
Mostly cloudy- light wind- no algae- weeds high- 3" rain last 10 days- 90 F + week.
Clear day- no wind- no algae- light rain last 2 weeks- weeds low due to cutting.
Clear day. 1/2" rain yesterday.  Cool 50 F.  Few boats on lake.
Windy- clear sky- 65 degrees F- and the weeds are just starting.
Clear and calm- temperature below normal- 38 degrees F at 6:00 pm- weeds high and being cut.
Windy- partly cloudy- 70 degrees F- and very light traffic on the lake.
Partly cloudy- warm- 80+ degrees- weeds being cut- and some algae.
Some clouds- cool- 60 degrees F- lots of leaves on the lake- and no boats.
Clear- calm- floating weeds. Still cutting
Partly cloudy- calm. No algae. Eurasian water milfoil in Bass Lake
Clear- slight wind. Lots of rain last few days. Frost this morning.
30' temperature 44 F.  1' temperature 56 F.  Sky partly cloudy- cool.  No weeds.
34' temperature 43 F.  1' temperature 76 F.  Clear sky.  84 F.  Heavy boat traffic.
35' temperature 43 F- 1' temperature 78 F.  Hazy sky.  High weeds.
34.5' temperature 45 F.  1' temperature 76 F.  Clear- calm.
Partly cloudy- calm.  Heavy rain last week.
Partly cloudy- slight wind- very few weeds.  Too cold.
Sunny but cool.  Low weed growth.  Not much cutting.
Mostly cloudy - slight rain last night.
Sunny- cool- 48 F.  Hard freeze yesterday.  24 F- calm.
Partly sunny- calm- little boat traffic.  Outside air low 45 F.
Partly cloudy- warm.  Slight wind.  Few boats.
Clear skies- slight wind.  Some weeds showing.
Clear skies- 50 F.  No boats- some floating weeds.
Partly cloudy- slight wind- 56 F.  Heavy rain last 2 weeks 9".
Heavy Boat traffic on weekend and Monday
Sunny- 69F- No boats- weed growing out top water
Clear sky- sunny- 80F- lots of weeds- heavy boat traffic on weekend
Satellite Path 24- Partly sunny- breezy- 71.5F- water temp @ 1ft: 73F
Ice out April 2.  Loons are back.  Sunny.  Temp. 65.3 F.
Sunny- light breeze.  68.8 F.  Heavy boat use all summer.
Sunny- light breeze.  Temp 66.4 F.  No boats today.  Loons are gone.
Partly sunny.  Lite breeze.  No boats today.  72.2 F temperature.
Sunny- 50 degrees F- windy. Ice out 4/28/2008
